================================================================================

The production daemon Docker image bundles ONNX weights derived from:

  iiiorg/piiranha-v1-detect-personal-information
  https://huggingface.co/iiiorg/piiranha-v1-detect-personal-information

Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0 (the "License"); you may
not use these weights except in compliance with the License. You may obtain
a copy of the License at:

  http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0

The weights are exported from the upstream PyTorch checkpoint to ONNX (and
optionally quantized to int8) at image build time. No modifications are made
to the model architecture or training data.

